<p>John and Dave have put together a fantastic show for you this week. They talk about how to verify Time Machine backups, managing swap &mdash; and sleep &mdash; files on your Mac, how and why to create a new user test account, checking your power consumption, how to use multiple sets of speakers simultaneously, throttling bandwidth on your (or someone else&rsquo;s Mac) and lots lots more. Download today for free and enjoy!</p>
